      "span_text": "In this sense, [CITATION_1] argued that if environmental certifications are not coupled with the actual implementation of the prescribed practices, firms may not be able to provide credible information to their buyers and sellers about their environmental stance, which increases information asymmetries and their subsequent drawbacks."
